        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick, with a matching lid), with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> and cook for 4 min, turning occasionally until the chicken is browned</p><p>Once browned, transfer the chicken to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
